{"tid":2133602,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"6月14日戴耀廷：已經預咗會dq，甚至贏咗都會dq","createTime":"2020-07-31T07:51:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T11:20:33.000Z","uid":48083,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b12c976fd3451c320d43ec861673cc6fc0a8c017","tid":2133602,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T07:51:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2DpBUqP5qxA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2DpBUqP5qxA&d=LJfbHi1nzQR09hbgKwAG129V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=5a41826b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2DpBUqP5qxA</a><br />\n<br />\n4:20開始<br />\n<br />\n白痴白粉打完稻草人未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df13a394fd16eedcdbeaf90a1c07b768d1b1dbda","tid":2133602,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T07:54:16.000Z","msg":"3月21日：<br />\n<br />\n中央若 DQ 將反證議會路線無效<br />\n<br />\n至於過去為何未能做到，沈旭暉認為有許多原因，例如人手、政治計算、社會未覺醒等。他認為比起探討原則價值問題，更應著眼於議席過半可能帶來的改變。他又說，功能組別和提名特首的選委會組成有一定關係，有機會繞過中央作出內部改變。<br />\n<br />\n對於中央有可能取消相關議員資格（ DQ ），甚至不委任，他形容若中央大規模干預，甚至改變整體結果，會是「破局」，證明議會路線已無效，未必是壞事，亦可能引起國際社會反彈，但「乜都唔做就只會 stuck 喺到」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/論民主派議席過半-沈旭暉-功能組別是關鍵-黃之鋒-不再鷸蚌相爭便有望/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E8%AB%96%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B4%BE%E8%AD%B0%E5%B8%AD%E9%81%8E%E5%8D%8A-%E6%B2%88%E6%97%AD%E6%9A%89-%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%B5%84%E5%88%A5%E6%98%AF%E9%97%9C%E9%8D%B5-%E9%BB%83%E4%B9%8B%E9%8B%92-%E4%B8%8D%E5%86%8D%E9%B7%B8%E8%9A%8C%E7%9B%B8%E7%88%AD%E4%B